

   THE PLAYER CARD AID FOR <- COVERT ACTION -> TYPED BY SCOOTER/SKID ROW
   =======================    -------------    =========================
   
   GENERAL
   -------
FUNCTION                  KEYBOARD                      JOYSTICK
--------                  --------                      --------
CHANGE MENU HIGHLIGHT     NUMERIC KEYPAD/ARROW KEYS     PULL/PUSH JOYSTICK
CHOOSE MENU OPTION        RETURN KEY/SPACE BAR          FIRE BUTTON      
LEAVE MENU OR SCREEN      ESCAPE KEY 
ANIMATIONS ON/OFF         ALT + A KEYS
JOYSTICK ON/OFF/RESET     ALT + J KEYS
PAUSE/RESTART GAME        ALT + P KEYS
QUIT GAME                 ALT + Q KEYS
SOUND ON/OFF              ALT + S KEYS

COMBAT/BREAK-INS
----------------
FUNCTION
--------
EXAMINE;OPEN;CLOSE        F1                            FIRE BUTTON
TAKE PHOTO                F2
TAKE PLUG                 F3
ENTER COMPUTER PASSWORD   F4
SHORT GRENADE THROW       F5
MEDIUM GRENADE THROW      F6
LONG GRENADE THROW        F7
(REMOTE CONTROL SETS OFF
(GRENADES)                F8
SET GRENADES              F9
SELECT GRENADE            F10
MOVE IN A DIRECTION       KEYPAD                        PULL/PUSH JOYSTICK
JUMP IN A DIRECTION       SHIFT + KEYPAD 
CROUCH/STAND UP           5 KEY
FIRE GUN                  SPACE BAR
FAST GAME SPEED           F KEY
DEFAULT GAME SPEED        D KEY
SLOW GAME SPEED           S KEY

CAR DRIVING CONTROLS
--------------------
FUNCTION
--------
INCREASE CAR SPEED        +/= KEY
DECREASE CAR SPEED        _/- KEY
CAR TURNS                 KEYPAD/ARROW KEYS
SWITCH CAR UNDER CONTROL  SPACE BAR
ARREST SUSPECT            F1 
ESCAPE INTO BUILDING      F2 
FOLLOW SUSPECT CAR        F10
FAST GAME SPEED           F KEY
DEFAULT GAME SPEED        D KEY
SLOW GAME SPEED           S KEY
QUIT CHASE                ESCAPE

WIRE-TAPPING/CAR TRACING CONTROLS
---------------------------------
FUNCTION                   
--------
MOVE HIGHLIGHT           KEYPAD/ARROW KEYS              PULL/PUSH JOYSTICK
REPLACE CHIP             RETURN KEY                     FIRE BUTTON

CODE BREAKING CONTROLS
----------------------
FUNCTION
--------
SELECT CODE LETTER          LETTER KEY
SELECT REPLACEMENT LETTER   LETTER KEY
ERASE REPLACEMENT LETTER    SPACE BAR
COMPUTER ASSISTANCE         F1 KEY
ERASE ALL GUESSES           F10 KEY

